high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the egg that's in front of you.
Turn right and take a step then turn right and take a step then turn right.
Wash the egg in the left sink then get it back out and shut off the water.
Turn right and walk to the wall then turn left.
Put the egg in the fridge under the mug.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean egg in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and face the counter to the left of the microwave.
Pick the egg up from the counter.
Move to the left and face the sink.
Put the egg in the sink on the left and turn the water on and then off and take the egg back out of the sink.
Turn around and turn to the left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the egg in and shut the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean egg in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter above the washing machine
Grab the egg that is on the counter
Turn around and go to the sink
Wash the egg in the sink and then take it out
Turn around and go to the fridge
Put the egg in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Putting an egg in the fridge
